refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.returnvalues;


 A pseudo random value between min
 (or 0) and max (or getrandmax, inclusive).

&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     7.2.0

      rand has received a bug fix for a modulo bias bug. This means that sequences generated with a specific seed may differ from PHP 7.1 on 64-bit machines.




     7.1.0

      rand has been made an alias of mt_rand.

  &reftitle.examples;



    rand example


<?php
echo rand(), "\n";
echo rand(), "\n";

echo rand(5, 15), "\n";
?>


